This project uses [graphify](https://github.com/safishamsi/graphify). Outputs live in `graphify-out/` (see `GRAPH_REPORT.md` in git; heavier artifacts are local only).

- Before architecture or “how is this wired?” questions, read `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` (god nodes, communities, surprises).
- If `graphify-out/wiki/index.md` exists, use it as the entry index instead of spelunking the repo blindly.
- After substantive code changes in the session, refresh the AST graph: **`npm run graphify:ast`** (fast, no LLM). Use full `/graphify` via `.cursor/skills/graphify/SKILL.md` when you need docs, PDFs, or images merged in.
